column5: Hit my favorite rivermouth this morning, and, came up with this chrome beauty (belly full of smelt!!)  Beauty orange meat, going to be one yummy supper!!
Way to go Frankie Nice chrome for sure.... congrats Thanks for sharing Leechman
Nice look'n fishy perfect eating size Richard
Nice look'n fishy perfect eating size   Thanks, guys...love that fall chrome, and, if you are going to keep one or two, this is the time of year to do it.  That dark orange flesh is amazing.
That meat looks very rich and clean! Nice catch
